ReviewText:
I recently purchased Nescafe Original Decaff as I am trying to take better care of myself, and I have found that too many or overly caffeinated drinks give me a headache, therefore I opted for this alternative to give a try.

I was a bit sceptical to begin with, I love coffee and I love my daily coffee hit, I feared that without the caffeine intake, the drink would not taste as good. However, I was definitely pleasantly surprised to find that this was not the case.

The coffee easy to make, I simply spooned the instant coffee into my favourite mug, added some skimmed milk, stirred and then added boiling water from my kettle, stirring continuously. The end result was a creamy, rich coffee that looked and smelt amazing.

The coffee tasted incredible! And I'm going to put it out there - I couldn't taste any difference between this and my usual Nescafe caffeinated product! In fact, it tasted just as delicious and moreish. It was very satisfying and refreshing, and helped give me a morning boost to kick start my day. I honestly felt so much better for drinking the Original Decaff as I felt that I had less headaches from too much caffeine and I was able to drink it without worrying about the consequences or without feeling guilty.

Overall, I highly rate this product - it gives you all the aroma, flavour and taste of Nescafe coffee but without all the caffeine! It's definitely a healthier option, one that makes life easier and is really delicious! It has a great, strong flavour with no caffeine but at no loss to the quality of the drink!
Title: Nescafe Decaff - All the flavour, no loss!
